"version": "1.0.4",
"title": "標題：女兒牆、擋土牆（parapet, retaining wall）",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3.1.5.1",
"language": "zht",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.1.5.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.1.5.1</span> 標題：女兒牆、擋土牆（parapet, retaining wall）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַעֲקֶה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ma‘aqeh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:8\">DEU 22:8</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>女兒牆是繞著房屋的平頂一圈建造的低矮石牆，用來防止人或物品從上面掉下來。參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1 房子、永久性住所 (house, permanent dwelling)&lt;REALIA:3.1&gt;</a> 中的插圖。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>大多數譯本都使用單個詞語來翻譯希伯來文<em>ma‘aqeh</em> ，例如「女兒牆」（“parapet”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）和「欄杆」（“railing”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 的「矮牆」（“low wall”）和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Spanish Common Language Version (Dios Habla Hoy)\">SPCL</abbr> 的「防護牆」都是很好的翻譯。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:8\">DEU 22:8</a> 的上下文清楚說明了女兒牆的目的，正如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 的譯法，英文意為：「你建造新房子時，要確保在屋頂的邊緣一周安上欄杆。這樣，即使有人摔下來死了，你也不用負責任。」在可能和必要的情況下，最好添加一個腳註，說明以色列人屋頂的樣式和用途（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.5 屋頂、房頂 (roof, housetop)&lt;REALIA:3.1.5&gt;</a> ）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
